      В· exact pinching_commutes (statePow ПҒ n) (вҶ‘(@SteinsLemma.Пғ''вңқ О№ instвңқ i ПҒ Оө m Пғ n))
      В· positivity
      В· positivity
      В· exact Пғ''_posdef ПҒ Оө m Пғ n
    have hE1proj : E1 Оө2 n = вҶ‘((в„° n) (statePow ПҒ n)).proj_lt (Real.exp (вҶ‘n * (ENNReal.toReal (@SteinsLemma.R1вңқ О№ instвңқ i ПҒ Оө) + Оө2)) вҖў вҶ‘(@SteinsLemma.Пғ''вңқ О№ instвңқ i ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)) := by
      unfold E1
